{"tid":1381773,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"防速龍大計！！","createTime":"2019-07-29T10:11:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T10:57:16.000Z","uid":192735,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"dd7cd3ba19ac6c21ceb3c9f6d68fc884a2638405","tid":1381773,"uid":192735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T10:11:33.000Z","msg":"想問如果見速龍想沖過黎，即刻開火計之術嚇下佢地得唔得？<br />\n<br />\n射程短但有阻嚇性<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />然後即走<br />\n<br />\n利申 睇緊侏羅紀公園🏃🏼&zwj;♂️         🦖<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=5pmlBp50XCw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5pmlBp50XCw&d=SfvWO4iieP9%2B5ivoSMB2BsRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=980d5286\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=5pmlBp50XCw</a>"},{"pid":"a109d7f3e04ef9264ca381a118b2006107b6f4ca","tid":1381773,"uid":26967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T10:13:04.000Z","msg":"[野狗野豬]大家要自保, 有實用工具<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1381553\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1381553</a>"},{"pid":"565009b8fee1b5c6b1aca5640bdce26ab0be7cf3","tid":1381773,"uid":22342,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T10:14:06.000Z","msg":"要用嗰下，用膠紙黐實粒掣保持持續性開火，擺低之後就走得"},{"pid":"851b94ad73103768ad7ae5cc3f68af91bf250077","tid":1381773,"uid":235580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T10:16:31.000Z","msg":"全部手足同我推！ 如何令黑警有所顧忌有所恐懼！ 如何從狗屋內部分解黑警！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1378251\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1378251</a>"},{"pid":"e5eb4b64aafe9afcb984a2637041c6f04a592209","tid":1381773,"uid":290530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T10:31:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fb9e99137e450b28a3b5617b5d0f44fb0f40a6a3","tid":1381773,"uid":42108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T10:35:47.000Z","msg":"唔係想鼓勵你地龜縮唔做嘢 小弟發夢都係企最前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過已經幾次死裏逃生覺得好多人都忽視左<br />\n比狗追咬嘅時候如果打唔贏要走應該點做<br />\n希望你地都可以討論一下諗下計仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n暫時諗到嘅係<br />\n<br />\n我極度希望前排嘅人<br />\n<br />\n你地齊裝嘅時候都唔該每人帶一個腰包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係背囊<br />\n即係下低呢個<br />\n又係decathlon<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.decathlon.com.hk/zh/p/500-ml/_/R-p-151313?mc=8547746&amp;c=黑色\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.decathlon.com.hk%2Fzh%2Fp%2F500-ml%2F_%2FR-p-151313%3Fmc%3D8547746%26c%3D%E9%BB%91%E8%89%B2&d=SfvWO4iieP9%2B5ivoSMB2BsRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=493e6929\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.decathlon.com.hk/zh/p/500-ml/_/R-p-151313?mc=8547746&amp;c=黑色</a><br />\n<br />\n點解？ 因為背囊根本唔適合緊急情況要攞嘢<br />\n同埋前線手足要攞其他工具係身<br />\n用腰包先可以裝到其他必要物資用黎撤退<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二樣嘢要講嘅就係入面應該裝乜嘢<br />\n我暫時諗到嘅就係<br />\n前線手足一唔係就用保鮮袋裝一包波子<br />\n或者用呢個<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z7x5GUu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz7x5GUu.png&h=b119a92f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n裝油或者蛋液<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家個問題就係當班狗衝上黎咬人而我地又唔夠打走緊嘅時候<br />\n欠缺一樣有效嘅方法減慢佢地逼進嘅速度<br />\n咁樣搞只會令到前線俾人當沙包咁咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好容易連累自己人<br />\n到依家為止，好多手足都仲係未有開始用呢堆工具<br />\n希望可以提多次大家<br />\n場夢未發完，我地要趁時間許可嘅時候準備充足d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"220293459805fc25fc6719c6703e03ed7a6ea8d0","tid":1381773,"uid":263161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T10:57:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}